    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0002",
      "text": " 72",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0003",
      "text": "The reporting port shall select ports from the registrant list for each Link Incident Record Format.  The",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        539.95,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0004",
      "text": "RLIR shall first be sent to all registered ports that have registered to always receive RLIRs.  If no reg-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        539.84,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0005",
      "text": "istered ports are registered to always receive RLIR or if RLIR was not successfully transmitted to at",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        540.02,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0006",
      "text": "least one of those ports registered to always receive RLIRs, then the reporting port shall send the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        93.65,
        539.92,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0007",
      "text": "RLIR to a registered port selected from among those that have registered to conditionally receive",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        105.64,
        539.94,
        116.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0008",
      "text": "RLIR.  If RLIR is not successfully transmitted to the selected registered port registered to conditional-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        117.64,
        540.07,
        128.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0009",
      "text": "ly receive RLIR, the sending port shall select another port, if any, from the established registration",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        129.64,
        539.91,
        140.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0010",
      "text": "list.  The RLIR ELS is considered successfully transmitted if a LS_ACC is received for the RLIR with-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        141.64,
        539.99,
        152.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0011",
      "text": "in 2xR_A_TOV.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        153.64,
        165.43,
        164.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0012",
      "text": "If a reporting port is not able to successfully deliver a RLIR ELS to a registered port, the registered",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        540.08,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0013",
      "text": "port’s registration for the incident port may be discarded.  If a reporting node is not able to successful-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        540.01,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0014",
      "text": "ly deliver an RLIR ELS through a particular reporting port, it may select a different reporting port and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        539.93,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0015",
      "text": "try again.  If no registration is established, it is vendor specific as to whether the incident port’s report-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        214.96,
        540.12,
        226.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p091_s0016",
      "text": "ing node generates and retains or discards the Link Incident Record.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        398.82,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
